{"ha42f53c3g5af3g47b9ga6b3g99fe66f418d6": ["*The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_005_Dead.html", "81f945e1-9662-2807-c67f-7b72ea0ea007"], "hc4190adbg3153g4548gb0adg58a4d0c85861": ["*The corpse regards you lifelessly.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_005_Dead.html", "f7773c93-cfb5-c442-2ff4-160da9b04a74"], "h5fb5bc4bg5cb1g4335g9d4bg775f62e925e7": ["Why did you go to the hag?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_005_Dead.html", "b0d10144-a68d-d469-c6fb-99043d08dd5d"], "h385c8f47g2af1g4ed2gba52g94bbebfa5417": ["My family took her... my baby girl...", "751644b1-44aa-4a85-944e-94419313d27f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_005_Dead.html", "63379841-a95e-1c48-e117-a9544150eeec"], "h931a523agb479g4ce9g8eb9g3a69dcb3c06a": ["Pretended she... never existed... ", "751644b1-44aa-4a85-944e-94419313d27f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_005_Dead.html", "ac3eb873-67f5-eb94-36c2-a67cd3d7e41d"], "h293d1912g87dbg4c54g984dg55c327d372c5": ["Told Ethel... never wanted... to see them again... she... took my eyes...", "751644b1-44aa-4a85-944e-94419313d27f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_005_Dead.html", "960096c9-598f-11e1-0820-cc1c498f5f3c"], "h09c4cc34g401fg4782ga54cg28a0b57f2d82": ["Why did your family take your child?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_005_Dead.html", "71a04451-0e91-f630-9286-734129054700"], "hbe85a899gbe97g4315gb4cegdf11923e0cec": ["They didn't like... me having something... they couldn't touch.", "751644b1-44aa-4a85-944e-94419313d27f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_005_Dead.html", "561c7b8b-f68c-c1aa-f663-6bd96ed18eb9"], "hfea5a352g0d84g4482gb358g80ba01a0efd3": ["What can you tell me about Ethel?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_005_Dead.html", "f071b915-35f4-816b-6896-9e987e1a6261"], "hc25b557dg5951g497bg90e3g1be2f3a851e5": ["... doesn't matter... nothing matters... without... baby girl...", "751644b1-44aa-4a85-944e-94419313d27f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_005_Dead.html", "731ecc5b-276b-3851-a9cd-486f2e73bc84"], "h94320afage9b6g45b2g85beg7c59ce16139b": ["Is there anything I should know about this place?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_005_Dead.html", "3ece0bfd-c74c-b574-2ad3-05b1ff819a02"], "h941e8f7dgc9b1g4f2dg8ae4g3f411f4aa11f": ["<i>Run</i>... ", "751644b1-44aa-4a85-944e-94419313d27f", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_005_Dead.html", "b4022f52-5ab6-f514-63e4-00969800096b"], "h9a47ac15gca11g4398ga92ag3c99358c9ec3": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_005_Dead.html", "7b809aa8-2100-10b5-1fb4-f787dd63c87a"], "h496f04e6gc2d9g4823g8b46g4dc4656b600d": ["*The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_HagLair_Victim_005_Dead.html", "18c05cae-f9b6-e749-b619-e44d1f7f16ef"]}